  "title": "[Woodlands- 5.5days] Warehouse Assistant (Pet Supplies)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Warehouse for pet supplies in Woodlands looking for Picker / Packer with the following job responsibilities:</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Basic: $2300</strong></p><p><strong>100% Attendance Incentive: $200</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Only Singaporean/PR</strong></p><ul><li><strong>5.5 days </strong></li><li>Stock taking and inventory updating and management</li><li>Receiving and checking when stocks arrival from Supplier</li><li>Picking and packing of goods for delivery</li><li>Ensure that warehouse is always neat and tidy</li><li>Assist in other ad-hoc duties as and when required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>1. Able to OT or work on certain weekend during sales period like 11/11,12/12,etc</p><p>3. must be able to pick, pack and count stocks when stocks arrive.</p><p>2. Physically fit to carry heavy items</p><p>You need to:</p><p>1. Possess positive attitude</p><p>2. Be a good team player</p><p>3. Be hardworking and honest</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>1. Good staff discount on pet merchandise</p><p>2. Attractive performance-based bonus</p><p>3. Overtime pay available</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Whatsapp or SMS: </strong><a href=\"tel:9654 9923\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>9654 9923</strong></a><strong> (Please do not call)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p></p><p></p><p>宠物店货仓招聘一名仓库管理员。工作范围：</p><p>1. 货仓管理, 检查及点算等任务</p><p>2. 包装，组装货物</p><p>3. 其它仓库任务</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>必须有：</strong></p><p>1. 拥有积极工作态度</p><p>2. 有团队精神</p><p>3. 勤劳，诚实</p><p><strong>福利:</strong></p><p>1. 宠物商品员工优惠</p><p>2. 依照工作表和公司业绩发年终奖金</p><p>3. 加班补贴</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Whatsapp or SMS: </strong><a href=\"tel:9654 9923\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>9654 9923</strong></a><strong> (Please do not call)</strong></p><p><strong>Only Singaporean/PR</strong></p>",
